room_title: Escape room "Cannibal" by Mind Twist in Las Vegas
room_address: 3200 S Las Vegas Blvd #1835 Las Vegas, NV 89109
room_description:
Hannibal Lector, the infamous cannibalistic serial killer has been behind bars for years, but it seems he has an admirer who is determined to become just as notorious.

Will you be able to outwit Dr. Lector and his protégé? Or are you about to participate in the worst dinner of your life?
